## 1. What Is FlowBoard?

FlowBoard is a production-grade containerized task management REST API built as the Node.js
Part 2 capstone project at Stratpoint. It uses every technology covered in Part 2: TypeScript,
Express, Prisma, PostgreSQL, Redis, Docker, Pino, Jest, and Nginx â€” all wired together in a
five-service Docker Compose stack.

