## 8. Rate Limiting

Applied only to `POST /auth/login` and `POST /auth/register`.

- Redis key: `rate:auth:{ip}`
- Window: 15 minutes (900 seconds)
- Limit: 100 requests per window
- Over limit: 429 `{ "success": false, "code": "RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED" }`
- Redis down: fail-open (log warning, call `next()` â€” do not block traffic)

