## 10. Logging (Pino)

Logger config (`api/src/lib/logger.ts`):

```typescript
pino({
  level: process.env.LOG_LEVEL ?? 'info',
  redact: [
    'req.headers.authorization',
    'body.password',
    'body.token',
    'body.refreshToken',
  ],
  transport: process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production'
    ? { target: 'pino-pretty' }
    : undefined,
})
```

**No `console.log` or `console.error`** anywhere in `api/` or `worker/`. Use `logger.info`,
`logger.warn`, `logger.error`.

