## 12. Security Rules

- No hardcoded secrets â€” all sensitive values come from environment variables
- All request bodies validated by Zod schemas with `.strict()` â€” unknown fields trigger 422 VALIDATION_ERROR (not silently dropped)
- Path params (IDs) validated as UUIDs via Zod
- `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` â€” 413 for oversized bodies
- `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` â€” correct IP extraction behind Nginx
- No stack traces in error responses when `NODE_ENV=production`
- bcrypt cost factor: 12

